        "mainSubtitle": "Overview",
        "mainTitle": "Redefining the future of Healthcare Tourism in The Kingdom of Saudi Arabia",
        "mainDescription": "SAGE is a pioneering healthcare concierge dedicated to transforming medical tourism in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. We move beyond simple logistics to build robust, structured systems and strategic partnerships that fundamentally enhance the entire patient journey. Our commitment is a direct alignment with Vision 2030, leveraging national ambition to elevate the quality of life and global medical standards.",
        "tagline": "Our Vision",
        "title": "Saudi Arabia as a Global Medical Hub",
        "description": "At Sage, we hold a clear and powerful vision: Saudi Arabia as the premier global destination for medical excellence—a place where patients from every corner of the world receive exceptional care within a culturally rich and welcoming environment.\n\nOur mission transcends basic coordination; we aim to deliver structured, world-class healthcare experiences that secure the patient's wellbeing.\n\nIn line with the Kingdom's visionary goals, we are actively building a fully integrated healthcare ecosystem through strategic alliances, advanced technological systems, and strict adherence to international standards. Our ultimate goal is to simplify the medical travel journey while ensuring every patient and partner receives personalized attention and trusted, transparent support.\n\nThrough innovation, absolute transparency, and a relentless commitment to excellence, we are redefining healthcare for global patients and partners alike—positioning Saudi Arabia as a beacon of healing, stability, and leadership in the global healthcare economy.",
